        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1609331310" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer2640101431232798692">Actual Rating: 4.5 stars<br/><br/><a href='http://wickedjr89sbookblog.blogspot.com/2017/10/the-pilo-family-circus-by-will-elliott.html' rel='nofollow noopener'>My full review &amp; more on my blog!</a><br/><br/>TW: Homophobia, Fire, Death, Animal Abuse (and death), Murder, Language, Self-Harm, R-word, Drugs<br/><br/>I&apos;m not really sure what to say about this book, other than I loved it! It&apos;s horrorific at times, funny at others and tugged at my heart at other times still. It&apos;s fast-paced, or maybe that&apos;s me as I read it in 3 days because Spookathon. Still I was entertained and wanting to know what was going to happen through-out the entire book. It occasio</span>
  <span id="freeText2640101431232798692" style="display:none">Actual Rating: 4.5 stars<br /><br /><a href="http://wickedjr89sbookblog.blogspot.com/2017/10/the-pilo-family-circus-by-will-elliott.html" rel="nofollow noopener">My full review &amp; more on my blog!</a><br /><br />TW: Homophobia, Fire, Death, Animal Abuse (and death), Murder, Language, Self-Harm, R-word, Drugs<br /><br />I'm not really sure what to say about this book, other than I loved it! It's horrorific at times, funny at others and tugged at my heart at other times still. It's fast-paced, or maybe that's me as I read it in 3 days because Spookathon. Still I was entertained and wanting to know what was going to happen through-out the entire book. It occasionally made me think. The writing was easy to read.<br /><br />I fell in love with Jamie. The characters felt well done to me for their purposes. The plot and world-building really shined to me. I fell in love with the carnival! In a weird way sure, but still. Writing a review is difficult for this book but not for lack of love for it! If this sounds at all up your alley give it a shot! I can't wait to get the sequel!<br /><br /><a href="https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCKrRV8TLtAL6nSL0W-Cs42w" rel="nofollow noopener">My Booktube Channel</a></span>
