<span id="freeTextContainer288590950803642716">These crazy clowns cause such a ruckus.<br/>It&apos;s not your average circus.<br/>They present false smiles,<br/>in painted faces.<br/>Trip you up<br/>with knotted laces.<br/>They make strange noises,<br/>peeps and whines.<br/>This job ain&apos;t no joke.<br/>It&apos;s a real crime.<br/>Do what you&apos;re told, <br/>Don&apos;t make the Pilo&apos;s blue.<br/>Step on their toes,<br/>and it&apos;s the funhouse for you.<br/><br/>by Nikki<br/><br/>It wasn&apos;t my mug of coffee. I didn&apos;t get the horror of it all. Yes, it had its psycho moments, but there was a lot of repetition. Boring day in and day out stuff. They put</span>
  <span id="freeText288590950803642716" style="display:none">These crazy clowns cause such a ruckus.<br />It's not your average circus.<br />They present false smiles,<br />in painted faces.<br />Trip you up<br />with knotted laces.<br />They make strange noises,<br />peeps and whines.<br />This job ain't no joke.<br />It's a real crime.<br />Do what you're told, <br />Don't make the Pilo's blue.<br />Step on their toes,<br />and it's the funhouse for you.<br /><br />by Nikki<br /><br />It wasn't my mug of coffee. I didn't get the horror of it all. Yes, it had its psycho moments, but there was a lot of repetition. Boring day in and day out stuff. They put on maybe two clown shows that were described? Maybe if I experienced it from a human attending the circus I would have gotten more out of it. The idea was great. The execution was not.<br /><br /></span>
