        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer82188837" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer17731983887793435601">If nothing else, <i>The Pilo Family Circus</i> will be as original a horror novel as you will ever read. Sporting equal parts of Dante&apos;s Inferno and the Barnum &amp; Bailey Circus, Will Elliott&apos;s surreal clown story will probably give you nightmares for a few nights. There has always been something dark about clowns and carnivals yet the author up the ante considerably on bad dreams and clown phobias. Part straight horror story and part hallucinogenic nightmare, this is a horror read that won&apos;t go away aft</span>
  <span id="freeText17731983887793435601" style="display:none">If nothing else, <i>The Pilo Family Circus</i> will be as original a horror novel as you will ever read. Sporting equal parts of Dante's Inferno and the Barnum &amp; Bailey Circus, Will Elliott's surreal clown story will probably give you nightmares for a few nights. There has always been something dark about clowns and carnivals yet the author up the ante considerably on bad dreams and clown phobias. Part straight horror story and part hallucinogenic nightmare, this is a horror read that won't go away after you turn the lights back on. </span>
  <a data-text-id="17731983887793435601" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
