        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer739159011" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer7365727150695272147">I fucking hate clowns. I really do. When I was a kid I had ring side seats at a circus and a stupid clown smashed an egg on my head, it poured down my face and all over my clothes. Everybody thought this was hilarious and pointed and laughed at me. I was very shy and was mortified. So I wanted to hate this book but I didn&apos;t, it was great. Its completely bonkers and great fun. I&apos;m already looking forward to the sequel I might even order it today. Fucking clowns!!!!!!!!</span>
  <span id="freeText7365727150695272147" style="display:none">I fucking hate clowns. I really do. When I was a kid I had ring side seats at a circus and a stupid clown smashed an egg on my head, it poured down my face and all over my clothes. Everybody thought this was hilarious and pointed and laughed at me. I was very shy and was mortified. So I wanted to hate this book but I didn't, it was great. Its completely bonkers and great fun. I'm already looking forward to the sequel I might even order it today. Fucking clowns!!!!!!!!</span>
